@@text-align:center;
Fit $$\theta$$ to minimize $$ \sum_i w^i (y^i - \theta^Tx^i)^2$$

where $$w^i = exp(-\frac{(x^i-x)^2}{2\tau^2})$$

if $$|x^i-x|$$ is small then $$w^i \approx 1$$ 

if $$|x^i-x|$$ is large then $$w^i \approx 0$$ 
